This translation is an unofficial derivative work of the
"PoE2 Enhanced User Interface" mod by Spherikal
(https://github.com/Spherikal/PoE2-EnhancedUserInterface).

The original mod does not publish an explicit license. This translation
is offered to the community on a best-effort basis under the same
implicit terms as the original mod: free to use, distribute and modify
for personal and community purposes, with credit to the original author.

If the upstream author objects to the redistribution of this translation,
please open an issue on this repository and it will be taken down or
adjusted.

The .stringtable files in this repository contain text derived from:
  - the structure of the original mod (© Spherikal and contributors)
  - the official French localization of Pillars of Eternity II: Deadfire
    (© Obsidian Entertainment / Versus Evil)

No game assets, no source from the base game, and no English-language
mod files are redistributed here — only the French translation strings
needed to localize the mod once it is already installed.
